  "prompt": "How do I start a digital marketing agency?",
  "response": "Here are key steps to start a digital marketing agency:\n\n1. Develop Your Skills\n- Master digital marketing techniques\n- Learn SEO, social media, content marketing\n- Get certifications (Google Analytics, HubSpot)\n\n2. Define Your Niche\n- Choose specific industries or services\n- Specialize in areas like:\n- B2B marketing\n- E-commerce marketing\n- Social media management\n- PPC advertising\n\n3. Business Planning\n- Create a business plan\n- Set pricing structure\n- Determine startup costs\n- Define target market\n\n4. Legal Requirements\n- Register your business\n- Get necessary licenses\n- Set up business bank account\n- Consider business insurance\n\n5. Build Initial Portfolio\n- Do pro-bono work\n- Create case studies\n- Develop sample marketing materials\n- Build professional website showcasing services\n\n6. Marketing Your Agency\n- Use LinkedIn networking\n- Create content marketing strategy\n- Attend industry events\n- Leverage referrals\n- Use social media marketing\n\n7. Tools and Infrastructure\n- Invest in marketing tools\n- Project management software\n- Analytics platforms\n- Communication tools\n\n8. Hire/Collaborate\n- Start with freelancers\n- Build network of specialists\n- Gradually hire full-time employees\n\n9. Continuous Learning\n- Stay updated on digital marketing trends\n- Attend workshops\n- Take advanced courses",
